title: Chanoso's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Downtown restaurant offering American-Asian fusion food with some veggie items, such as the Kentucky fried tofu, edamole (edamame avocado) dip, crispy cauliflower fritters, caesar salad with crispy tofu and coconut bacon, vegetable sushi, stirfry, red lentil soup, and daily specials. Be sure to specify veg.
